ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:09:15.000Z","msg":"以前覺得難以理解同接受。<br />\n<br />\n而家覺得呢個係人性。事實放在眼前時，只能處理。"},{"pid":"fbbcda559ea47ac03be0a4e828d0933c576eb39e","tid":2189212,"uid":7288,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T23:18:06.000Z","msg":"唔會原諒，但未離開/離婚前盡量保持距離<br />\n先分手/離婚，或者都會當自己單身，<br />\n遇到下個跟得過嘅就走<br />\n<br />\n眼前嘅人傷害自己，唔會保護你係100%事實<br />\n但搵下個都仲有50/50機會"},{"pid":"72b418cb3c933fee16c64a0196a2e59cdcedef15","tid":2189212,"uid":214635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6a30932142baf24cf72a673317edc2c85f000ee0","tid":2189212,"uid":156587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T21:01:54.000Z","msg":"好想答會 但無奈地你個心一定有條刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"仲好撚痛，一齊返睇返佢紀錄，爆房app又有，酒店app仲要就埋人地返工果區過夜，有仔女都唔想一齊返，無仔女做乜仲要一齊返呢？"},{"pid":"1fe854c256b7fccbc0a3c9141e78dd9387589ee7","tid":2189212,"uid":2470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:21:42.000Z","msg":"會原諒"},{"pid":"fb45379251bcb328b7c52ea97de4d968eac31387","tid":2189212,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:23:45.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n中出等佢有左<br />\n再屌到佢唔想俾我屌<br />\n到時等佢飛我"},{"pid":"88adaa71d735c54276cebf3c3a10df4656eac044","tid":2189212,"uid":288013,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T00:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔會囉，除非雙方都同意開放式關係，否則一個控制能力咁差既人要黎做咩，對自己既幸福都唔識負責，更何況對人？何必難為自己成就段爛桃花，除非睇得電影小說，以為愛情要驚天動地lol"},{"pid":"288f78fc4ce08221899fcbc808ff078d99d55211","tid":2189212,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f3e857ee895764d1c86daaf46af7012a03558454","tid":2189212,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T20:00:29.000Z","msg":"樓主係巴定絲？<br />\n<br />\n如果精神出軌，你會唔會覺得一定完？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"絲， 所以我打肉體，<br />\n精神上我仲諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c964ba2f6d72761e4792154e63646730095ac9","tid":2189212,"uid":2470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"當你愛佢 大家都想挽回 就會刻服到<br />\n愛係包容"},{"pid":"759484577277121a9901595a46da2e295f59186c","tid":2189212,"uid":345160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"曾經嘅我都以為自己係咁灑脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaa76b9ba9a3cf13e4ba779caa75ec2316d3dc4","tid":2189212,"uid":252264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"愛佢 都原諒佢<br />\n但無信心佢會改 同點都有條刺 好無安全感<br />\n所以唔會一齊返"},{"pid":"d74e0106c27bd4908ff9375ee486775a992ce114","tid":2189212,"uid":180039,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"21384693a0671ddea17109c8b3223673a4720db7","tid":2189212,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"750613777ce1dcdae476e77d1776c4d085154e27","tid":2189212,"uid":180039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T21:11:50.000Z","msg":"男朋友 仲可以原諒<br />\n結婚對象/ 老公： 一次都唔會原諒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T21:27:39.000Z","msg":"反而係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越重視越原諒唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好大可能係果個人出得軌已經係唔鍾意你<br />\n你原諒佢<br />\n佢都唔想同你一齊<br />\n反正都撕破個面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"因為一次不忠 百次不容<br />\n如果去到就嚟結婚或者結咗婚都仲可以出軌<br />\n呢種背叛令到以後點都唔會再有信任<br />\n一個同自己過人世嘅人<br />\n要用成世時間成日懷疑佢 擔心佢<br />\n自己都好易殘 仲好易痴線 好辛苦<br />\n所以長痛不如短痛<br />\n反而拍拖，未當對方係結婚對象<br />\n原諒佢之後去到要分手果段時間會容易過啲"},{"pid":"cf12238f47bd1f8c8b09ec669f8e41931dae7aad","tid":2189212,"uid":332795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"寧願肉體出軌都唔好精神出軌<br />\n性同愛根本就係兩回事<br />\n關係係建立係愛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時諗緊人類根本唔適合一夫一妻制<br />\n再鍾意一個人 肉體上幾年就會悶"},{"pid":"b8a83317e06fb0f82ece65670210cacd4356eb18","tid":2189212,"uid":9863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"如果大家都接受到對方肉體出軌<br />\n其實有幾愛呀？可以有幾愛呀？<br />\n可以好愛但少少佔有慾都冇？<br />\n假設兩個都接受到<br />\n我會覺得佢地一齊只係為咗維持有對方喺身邊嘅生活<br />\n而唔係愛"},{"pid":"fbbd82f98ac4d6bcddebc410c814a6e238b40a8c","tid":2189212,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"肯俾我偷睇住佢NTR咪原諒囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38d532e7f65f483566d05a784e47c650d842e07","tid":2189212,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"如果結咗婚有仔女嘅話會嘗試下原諒，除咗呢個情況之外應該都會即刻斬纜"},{"pid":"8e6863ac436b945e556538fbc0543d30454a55c3","tid":2189212,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:34:55.000Z","msg":"一次不忠 百次不用"},{"pid":"3446791d1d66fa4ca4d6a70e627060f267b3e96f","tid":2189212,"uid":57439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"未婚就分<br />\n<br />\n已婚就算, 一世人對住同一件好辛苦又悶, 出軌都係想透下氣<br />\n如果淨出軌又繼續到夫妻關係咪尤佢"},{"pid":"ffbae00600dfc1b2d725c1f1ce7815219ae6116d","tid":2189212,"uid":374520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"男朋友應該唔會原諒，老公可能會再觀察下"},{"pid":"66d55b669017e8dafc01e651ac37624c4c088541","tid":2189212,"uid":94148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"背叛過一次就永遠都信唔番"},{"pid":"f4724039496ce4fbe105f5e2e20cf0a6fd612bed","tid":2189212,"uid":244241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"呢排開始懷疑人生，開始覺得人類嘅天性可能根本唔適合一夫一妻制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be39483ee3a28e056c73bc443276551c395ed92","tid":2189212,"uid":296664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"傾好晒知道大家接受到咩嫁話唔係出軌<br />\n出軌等於背叛 如果加埋隱瞞欺騙嫁話 原唔原諒都對段關係好大影響 （信任係所有親密關係嘅基本要求 親人又好朋友又好情侶都好）<br />\n<br />\n除非去到有朝一日所有人都視性愛係完全分離 如果唔係時代點變遷都唔會接受到出軌"},{"pid":"5bb83a6853d736976ea7613b8155a9f5622439b7","tid":2189212,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n過來人<br />\n巴<br />\n<br />\n講唔會係女人<br />\n<br />\n男人多情而長情，女人專情而絕情"},{"pid":"4817b894f3659a381ff5725eb26c3fcfb3463a09","tid":2189212,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"又唔係處女俾幾多個人屌過都一樣嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keyKZfL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeyKZfL.gif&h=5fa2f4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔通咁樣又好咩<br />\n每個人都有缺點又唔洗特別放大一樣黎睇"},{"pid":"a4289b7964529efa1e21991ecd51c14c1bf9e111","tid":2189212,"uid":236904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"40-50歲可能會<br />\n40以下應該唔會"},{"pid":"1dfcb4763057833f8c562c42ff9a9f14903ecaa2","tid":2189212,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4817b894f3659a381ff5725eb26c3fcfb3463a09","tid":2189212,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"又唔係處女俾幾多個人屌過都一樣嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keyKZfL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeyKZfL.gif&h=5fa2f4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔通咁樣又好咩<br />\n每個人都有缺點又唔洗特別放大一樣黎睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"白卡婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錫果下覺得好sweet係咪我問題"}]}